data.description: Welcome to 16 Dogwood Drive, where charm abounds! Nestled on a corner, 2-acre estate lot in Dogwood Estates, this 5 bedroom/4.5 bath home complete with a personal pool has over 5100 finished square feet. Step inside to discover large living spaces, fireplace, hardwood floors, and abundant natural light. The kitchen boasts granite countertops and an eat in area. The main level master suite, office, 3 upstairs bedrooms and additional den, bedroom & bath in basement, provide ample space for everyone in the family. Enjoy outdoor living at its best with a fenced yard, perfect for children and pets, and an inviting in-ground pool for endless summer enjoyment. There's ample parking with two large driveways, 2-car main level garage, as well as an additional garage in the basement that is big enough for a workshop. Don't miss your chance to experience Southern living at its finest—Schedule your showing today!
